(397,'BROOKLYN BRIDGE PARK Fall 2025 Outdoor 9s','1',0,155,1850,9,12,3,3,'<p><strong>Note: A change to format meaning two (2) female players required on the outfield now.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Opening night for new registrant is September 23rd.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The games are 9-a-side requiring a goalkeeper and eight outfield players. While the ''keeper is non-gender specific, a minimum of TWO female players must constitute the outfield participants at all times.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Rosters should be a minimum of 12 players and take into account the on-field requirements. Captains can register by making an Individual Payment - teammates will then be able to register/pay individually prior to a deadline.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Payment of the one-time Team Fee allows 16 players on the official roster - Team Fees must be made as a one-off payment at the outset of registration.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>48 minute games and teams will have a minimum of 8 fixtures.</p>','','Tuesdays 6:30pm-9pm','2025-09-27',0,0,0,3,NULL,'/static/img/leagues/league-1.jpg',5,48,0,'COED','Pool Stage Competition',false,1);
