(398,'GANSEVOORT Fall 2025 Outdoor 7s','2',0,155,1600,7,11,2,3,'<p>Opening night is Wednesday September 3rd and 10th, depending upon your scheduling assignment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>LOCATION</strong>: Games are played at Gansevoort Peninsula Athletic Field, NY 10014 on the Hudson across from the Meatpacking District.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The games are 7-a-side requiring a goalkeeper and six outfield players. While the ''keeper is non-gender specific, a <strong>minimum of two female</strong> players must constitute the outfield participants at all times.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Rosters should be a minimum of 11 players and take into account the on-field requirements. Captains can register by making an Individual Payment - teammates will then be able to register/pay individually prior to a deadline.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Payment of the one-time Team Fee allows 15 players on the official roster - Team Fees must be made as a one-off payment at the outset of registration.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Games consist of 44 minutes of continuous play and teams will have a minimum of 7 fixtures.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Kick-offs will be 7pm and 7:45pm. Teams will rotate within these slots over the course of the season.</p>','','Games are played 7pm-8:30pm','2025-09-10',0,0,0,3,NULL,'/static/img/leagues/league-1.jpg',1,44,0,'COED','Pool Stage Competition',false,1);
